These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, baccarat
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the baccarat-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the game-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Cigar      | game  | baccarat   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Birthday     | january | october    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, sunflower
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Birthday   | march | august  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Flower     | balloon-flower   | sunflower    |

