.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, turkish
2 different games are played: poker, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the turkish is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Nationality          | turkish   | argentine  |
| Game         | poker | scrabble     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

